## Per-Project Secrets

| Project | Required vars | Production home |
|---------|---------------|----------------|
| [Project A] | `API_KEY`, `DB_URL` | [Platform] env vars |
| [Project B] | `SERVICE_KEY` | [Platform] env vars |

